text: Natalia "Natasha" Yarovenko (; born 23 July 1979) is a Ukrainian actress and model. She was born in Odesa, Ukraine. In 2011 Yarovenko won two awards for the Best New Actress for her role in the movie Room in Rome, one at the Turia Awards and the other at the 25th Goya Awards. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Goya Award winners Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian movie actors Category:Ukrainian television actors Category:Ukrainian models Category:Actors from Odesa
